    "Remove every ancestry-only path from HEAD while retaining it in history.",
    "Reduce package.json, pnpm-workspace.yaml and all cell-aware scripts to NOVA only.",
    "Regenerate pnpm-lock.yaml after all external artifacts pass live registry readback.",
    "Rewrite the Docker context and Dockerfile to install external packages instead of copying provider sources.",
    "Rewrite .github/workflows/nova.yml as a standalone workflow without _cell-ci.yml.",
    "Remove monorepo-only release, documentation, architecture and operations branches from retained neutral tooling."
